### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">وَإِنَّ مِنكُمْ لَمَن لَّيُبَطِّئَنَّ فَإِنْ أَصَـٰبَتْكُم مُّصِيبَةٌ قَالَ قَدْ أَنْعَمَ ٱللَّهُ عَلَىَّ إِذْ لَمْ أَكُن مَّعَهُمْ شَهِيدًا</span>

### English

There will be some among you who will lag behind so that if you face a disaster, they will say, “Allah has blessed us for not being there among them.”